Lightning Experience Adoption

Lightning Usage App provides Lightning Exp adoption metrics based on the usage, activity, and security
App Launcher| Lighnting Usage

⦁	Daily and monthly active users in Lightning Exp and the SF mobile app
⦁	Daily and monthly switches to SF Classic
⦁	Profiles and users that switched to SF Classic
⦁	Slowest desktop record pages
⦁	Browsers used to access Lightning Exp and SF mobile app
⦁	Pages viewed most often in Lightning Exp
⦁	Number of active users, featurs, and PS licenses

>System Overview for User Interface
Shows usage and limits

Sales Enablement
Is a process of education and guidance that gives members of sales team the skills and tools they need to succeed

Tech Debt
Is the extra work that accrues as a result of taking shortcuts or choosing a quicker and easier solution
This is accured when speed is prioritized over quality
In the long run more cost and time 

Future work
Technical Debt is not necessarily harmful to the org.
It can become time consuming and require a lot of effort to clean up or address at a later time
